        <mxCell id="-fp5AD1cwv2DQiWJSyQd-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Start Transit of Stocks In Warehouses&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;An Employee can add/decrease stocks in a Warehouse by starting a Transit of stocks from a Origin to a destination Warehouse. They choose a origin warehouse or external producer and adds stocks to a list from a list of available products from that warehouse/producer. They must supply quantity on each stock with a max being supply from origin warehouse or no max from producer. Employee must also supply if the transit is to be picked up at the warehouse.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="430" width="180" x="30" y="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
